        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4">
                <h3><i class="fa fa-question"></i> Why Wild-HomeLearn?</h3>
                <p>Wild HomeLearn is a non-profit online learning platform focusing on Australian ecosystems. We are committed to helping people learn about Australia's wildlife through our free policy. We focus on helping children living in Australia learn about their native wild animals and camping.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4">
                <h3><i class="fa fa-pencil"></i> Our Solution..is Belief</h3>
                <p>By analyzing children's preferences and learning characteristics, we designed interactive teaching models that are attractive to children. Children's attention is captured by video to study and learn about Australian wildlife, and the learning results are detected by interactive game mode to ensure the quality of children's learning.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4">
                <h3><i class="fa fa-folder-open"></i>Our Contents</h3>
                <p>We have visual data analysis, interactive learning experiences, lively instructional videos, responsive search engines and a rich database of Australian wildlife to provide reliable and interesting learning experiences and camping advice.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <hr>
    </div> 
